                                    <locus target="#16" facs="018">Fol. 16</locus> is split in half from top to bottom, down one of the creases of the center column. It is sewn together in two places.</note>
                              Quire 2
                              9 added
                            </item>
                              <item xml:id="q4" n="3">
                                 <dim unit="leaf">10</dim>
                                 <locus from="20" to="29" facs="022">Fols 20–29</locus>
